Our prototype successfully demonstrates a mobile application designed to help high school students in learning new topics/subjects using a structured learning process like roadmaps, it aligns well with our chosen SDG topic: SDG 4 (Quality Education).
The prototype features a clean UI that is also easy to navigate across the application's various features. During the testing phase, some aspects of the prototype were identified to be wrong or unsatisfactory according to testers. 
The prototype was then updated or modified according to user feedback to improve user experience as well as usability. 
